    <section id="our-mission" class="about-section">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <div class="mission-content">
        <div class="mission-text">
          <p>The Missing Person Finder platform was created with a simple yet powerful vision: to make the process of finding missing loved ones faster, more efficient, and more accessible to everyone. We believe that every missing person deserves to be found, and every family deserves closure.</p>
          <p>In today's digital age, we recognized that traditional methods of searching for missing persons were often slow, fragmented, and inaccessible to many. Our platform bridges these gaps by providing a centralized, user-friendly system that connects those who have lost someone with those who may have found them.</p>
          <p>We believe every missing case deserves attention. We created this with the hope of bringing people back home. Change starts with all of us. Let's be the reason someone is found.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-stats">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-number">1000+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Families Reunited</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-number">5000+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Active Cases</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-number">10,000+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Community Members</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="admin-team" class="about-section">
      <h2>Our Admin Team</h2>
      <div class="team-intro">
        <p>Our dedicated team of administrators works tirelessly to ensure that every case receives the attention it deserves. We understand the urgency and emotional toll of missing person cases, and we're committed to providing a platform that helps reunite families as quickly as possible.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="admin-message">
        <div class="message-icon">
