          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="message-content">
          <h3>Why We Created This Platform</h3>
          <p>We created the Missing Person Finder to provide a fast, efficient, and modern tool for handling missing person cases. Our platform simplifies case management and provides real-time visibility for everyone involved.</p>
          <p>This platform is built for the public, law enforcement, and families. We believe that technology should serve humanity, and our vision is to leverage technology to solve this critical social issue.</p>
          <p>Our platform addresses these issues by providing:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>A centralized database of missing and found person reports</li>
            <li>Real-time updates and notifications</li>
            <li>Easy-to-use interfaces for both reporting and searching</li>
            <li>Community engagement tools to amplify search efforts</li>
            <li>Secure information sharing between relevant parties</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We believe that by making the process faster and more accessible, we can help reunite more families and bring hope to communities. Every minute counts in a missing person case, and our platform is designed to save precious time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
